text: Adam Clarke (born 10 November 1981) is an English cricketer. He played three first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 2001 and 2004. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Sherwood, Nottingham Category:Cambridge MCCU cricketers
